column5: Shut up reading Order of the Phoenix

I have thought about that also. I work partly off of commission and the other stores are not as busy.  I just make much more money at my location. But at the end of the day, the other locations would definitely be less of a headache.

The sad part is that my District Manager also wants her out. My manager is in a extramarital affair with a higher up in my company. Hence why she feels invincible. But I have to do something. I'm only 27 and stressed way too much. So I will give it a try!

I was thinking of a recorder of some sort on my phone. The problem is that I do enjoy my line of work. But it's also starting stress in my relationship. My fiance knows how she treats me and gets pretty angry about it. So I have to do something soon. Thank you for the advice.
